commentAnnotations.text: Janssen Research & Development is a global organization that operates through different legal entities in various countries. The term 'sponsor' is used throughout the protocol to represent these various legal entities.

All subjects will undergo QuantiFERON-TB Gold testing. In countries where the QuantiFERON-TB Gold test is not registered/approved, TB skin testing will also be required (recommended but not required for study centers in Ukraine if tuberculin is not available).

commentAnnotations.text: The screening endoscopy must be performed within 2 weeks before the I-0 visit. The Mayo endoscopy subscore assessed by the central reader will be used to determine eligibility.
